import React from 'react';
import {Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap';
import Image from 'react-image-resizer';
var image = require('../images/check-icon-vector-10850982.jpg')
export default class GridContainer extends React.Component {
    render() {
        return(
            <Container>
                <Row >
                    <Col xs={3} md={1}>Company</Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1}>Personal Auto</Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1}>Personal Home</Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1}>Dwell fire</Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1}>Commercial BOP</Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1}>Commercial BAP</Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1}>Commercial WC</Col>
                </Row>
                <Row>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1} style={{justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                        <Image src={image} height={40} width={40}/>
                    </Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1} style={{justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                        <Image src={image} height={40} width={40}/>
                    </Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1} style={{justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                        <Image src={image} height={40} width={40}/>
                    </Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1} style={{justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                        <Image src={image} height={40} width={40}/>
                    </Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1} style={{justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                        <Image src={image} height={40} width={40}/>
                    </Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1} style={{justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                        <Image src={image} height={40} width={40}/>
                    </Col>
                    <Col xs={3} md={1} style={{justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                        <Image src={image} height={40} width={40}/>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        )
    }
}
